  scenario="It is 9:45am on a Thursday. You are on a domestic extension in Warrington — the cavity wall is going up and you have a concrete pour booked for the padstone at midday. Your phone buzzes in your hi-vis pocket but you cannot stop. A homeowner in Lymm has just had a surveyor condemn the chimney breast above her living room fireplace — the bricks are spalling and the flashing has failed. She needs someone who can rebuild the chimney stack and re-flash before winter. Without AI Phone Answering, she hears your voicemail, hangs up, and tries the bricklayer her surveyor recommended. With the AI, she hears: 'Good morning, thank you for calling, how can I help?' The AI captures the chimney issue, the urgency, her address, and her availability for a site visit. At lunch, you review the lead and call her back — she is relieved, books a visit for Saturday, and you win a job worth over two grand."
